        <content><![CDATA[ <h1 class="title topictitle1">Create an interactive filter</h1>  <div class="body taskbody"><div class="section context"><p class="p"><span class="ph">Interactive Filters allow you to filter   report widgets directly from a homepage or Performance Analytics dashboard without modifying the   reports.</span>    <span class="ph">You can create Interactive Filters for      multiple field types.</span></p></div>   <ol class="ol steps"><li class="li step stepexpand">    <span class="ph cmd">In the <span class="ph uicontrol">Filter based on</span> choice list, select a filter type.</span>   </li><li class="li step stepexpand">    <span class="ph cmd">Set the following fields if applicable. Some filter types do not require all fields.</span>    <div class="itemgroup info">Each filter type has specific required information.</div>    <table class="simpletable choicetable choicetableborder" id="sys_ui_hp_publisher-normal__choicetable_whs_5nl_d1b"><thead><tr class="sthead chhead"><th id="d402066e50-option">Name</th><th id="d402066e50-desc">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="strow chrow"><td id="d402066e63" class="stentry choption"><strong>Name</strong></td><td class="stentry chdesc">Enter a name for the filter. </td></tr><tr class="strow chrow"><td id="d402066e72" class="stentry choption"><strong>Look up name</strong></td><td class="stentry chdesc">Enter a lookup name for the filter. This name appears in the <span class="ph uicontrol">Add        content</span> menu for users adding a filter to a homepage or dashboard. </td></tr><tr class="strow chrow"><td id="d402066e84" class="stentry choption"><strong>Description</strong></td><td class="stentry chdesc">Enter a description of the filter.</td></tr><tr class="strow chrow"><td id="d402066e93" class="stentry choption"><strong>UI control type</strong></td><td class="stentry chdesc">Select how the available filtering options for this filter appear on the homepage       widget.</td></tr></tbody></table>   </li></ol>   </div> <div class="related-links"><div class="relinfo"><div class="reltitle">Related information<br /><div><a class="link" href="https://docs.servicenow.com/?context&#61;CSHelp:available-interactive-filter-types&amp;version&#61;jakarta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Available Interactive Filter types</a></div><div><a class="link" href="https://docs.servicenow.com/?context&#61;CSHelp:available-interactive-filter-ui-control-types&amp;version&#61;jakarta" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Available interactive filter UI control types</a></div></div></div></div>]]></content>
